item.title: Spotted this morning...
item.description: Spotted this morning… # in front of my office: Ever wondered how accurate navigable map data for your Garmin, your in-car navigation system (most likely), or maps.nokia.com are created? One piece of the puzzle is the car above collecting data for Navteq, a subsidary of Nokia.
